{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 3.\tx360\tab The GM determines the resistance. The GM opposes the PC with a resistance\u8212-the harder the task or tougher the opponent, the higher the resistance.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 4.\tx360\tab Roll a d20 to determine the PCs degree of success or failure, then apply any bumps. The GM does the same for the resistance. Compare your rolled number with your TN to see how well you succeeded or failed with your ability. Remember to apply any bumps from masteries or hero points.\par}
